(5, 1, '2018-12-06 13:50:49', '2018-12-06 13:50:49', '<h2><b>My Little Story</b></h2>		\n		<p>I have been an art creator since childhood. When those funny little drawings, created by me as a child became my passion I didn''t realize. But creation has been my life ever since. I have done my bachelors in Applied Arts from a ell known University. I worked as a designer for three years for a small firm and then went to work in the mainstream advertising.</p>		\n			<a href="http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/contact-me/" role="button">\n						About Me\n					</a>\n										<img width="525" height="531" src="http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img1-1.png" alt="" srcset="http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img1-1.png 800w, http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img1-1-297x300.png 297w, http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img1-1-768x777.png 768w, http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img1-1-100x100.png 100w" sizes="100vw" />											\n			<h3>ILLUSTRATOR</h3><p>I have been working in Illustrator for quite a long time now and it is great for vector and logo creations. All my projects always start within this software and I then take them forward.</p>		\n			<h3>PHOTOSHOP</h3><p>I have been gathered the skill of Photoshop over a long period of time. This was the first design software I learned and have enjoyed it ever since. None of my important photos can escape from this one.</p>		\n			<h3>SKETCH</h3><p>I have very recently started learning this software and it has made quite a few tasks simple for me. I will be diving more into the depths of this one. I find it very helpful when it comes to Web page creation.</p>		\n			<h3>WEB DEVELOPMENT</h3><p>I always thought coding was a task not for me. But after learning this I have realized the potential it holds. A designer is a nothing without a folio and in today''s era it has to be digital. Here I am creating mine.</p>		\n			<h2><b>IMAGINATION IS EVERYTHING\n<br></b>It is a preview of life''s coming attactions.</h2>		\n		<p>The life of a designer is a life of fight. Fight against the ugliness. Just like a doctor fights against disease. For us, the visual disease is what we have around, and what we try to do is cure it somehow with design.</p>		\n			<a href="http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/my-work/" role="button">\n						Check My Work\n					</a>\n							Projects\n							Designs\n							Clients\n										<img width="525" height="391" src="http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img2-1.png" alt="" srcset="http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img2-1.png 1019w, http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img2-1-300x223.png 300w, http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/img2-1-768x571.png 768w" sizes="100vw" />											\n			<h2>My Skills</h2>		\n		<ul><li>HTML</li><li>CSS</li><li>Logo Designing</li><li>Illustrator</li><li>Graphic Designing</li></ul>		\n							<a href="" target="_blank">\n					Facebook\n				</a>\n							<a href="" target="_blank">\n					Twitter\n				</a>\n							<a href="" target="_blank">\n					Google-plus\n				</a>\n							<a href="" target="_blank">\n					Instagram\n				</a>\n							<a href="" target="_blank">\n					Whatsapp\n				</a>\n				HTML\n									90%\n				CSS\n									80%\n				JAVASCRIPT\n									75%\n				PHOTOSHOP\n									95%\n				ILLUSTRATOR\n									100%\n				INDESIGN\n									80%', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2018-12-07 15:26:13', '2018-12-07 15:26:13', '', 0, 'http://localhost/MY_PROJECTS/suvidhaPortfolio/?page_id=5', 0, 'page', '', 0),
